Date: 1999-04-24

Title: Non linear realizations of isometry groups, conformal algebras and

geodesics in Anti-de Sitter like spacesComments: 13 pages, latex file, La Plata preprint Th-99/04

We present the explicit global realization of the isometries of anti-deSitter like spaces of signature $(d_-,d_+)$, and their algebras in the space offunctions on the pseudo-Riemannian symmetric space $SO(d_- +1,d_+) /SO(d_-,d_+)$. The process of going to the invariant boundaries leads to therealization of the corresponding conformal groups and algebras. We computesystematically the geodesics in these spaces by considering the cosetrepresentation of them.